{{共产党}}
'''科威特进步运动'''（{{lang-ar|الحركة التقدمية الكويتية}}）是[[科威特|科威特]]的一个[[左翼|左翼]]政党。该党的前身是1975年3月14日成立的科威特人民联盟。2011年3月14日，该党正式成立。该党的意识形态是[[科学社会主义|科学社会主义]]、[[反资本主义|反资本主义]]、[[反帝国主义|反帝国主义]]。该党的秘书长是{{link-ar|艾哈迈德·德亚因|أحمد الديين}}。该党的总部位于{{le|安达卢斯 (科威特)|Al Andalus, Kuwait|安达卢斯}}<ref>{{cite web|title=Q&A with the Kuwait Progressive Movement|url=http://www.yourmiddleeast.com/features/qa-with-the-kuwait-progressive-movement_12772|year=2013|work=yourmiddleeast.com|access-date=2020-08-02|archive-date=2016-09-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160930203223/http://www.yourmiddleeast.com/features/qa-with-the-kuwait-progressive-movement_12772|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Kuwait’s Opposition: Who Are They?|url=http://www.al-monitor.com/pulse/ar/politics/2012/10/who-are-kuwaits-opposition.html|work=Al Monitor|access-date=2020-08-02|archive-date=2016-06-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160602144804/http://www.al-monitor.com/pulse/ar/politics/2012/10/who-are-kuwaits-opposition.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Progressive Kuwaiti Movement Official Website|url=http://taqadomi.com/|language=阿拉伯语|access-date=2020-08-02|archive-date=2021-02-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210204170906/http://taqadomi.com/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite book|last=Cavatorta|first=Francesco|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=d398DwAAQBAJ&pg=PA2015&lpg=PA2015&dq=Kuwaiti+Progressive+Movement&source=bl&ots=WadEDgVcX6&sig=ACfU3U3tiH9WXgVHt3hKx2qJBNGsMnHeHg&hl=en&sa=X&ved=2ahUKEwjFztP10bzpAhXvIDQIHY6GCs8Q6AEwCXoECAkQAQ#v=onepage&q=Kuwaiti%20Progressive%20Movement&f=false|title=Political Parties in the Arab World: Continuity and Change|date=2018-06-30|publisher=Edinburgh University Press|isbn=978-1-4744-2409-7|language=en}}</ref>。

